{"tid":2191842,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"十個肥婆九個閪 剩低一個好撚nice","createTime":"2020-09-06T16:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T01:08:34.000Z","uid":371912,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e4da84fc34b41f15bd67acd07db94516ad5140ea","tid":2191842,"uid":371912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"唔知點解肥婆永遠都係咁乞人憎，總覺得肥婆都係最攻心計<br />\n<br />\n返學嘅時候 永遠講是非啲八婆永遠都係啲肥婆講先 篤背脊報串嗰啲呢永遠都係肥婆 <br />\n<br />\n依家出嚟做嘢 啲肥婆嘅上級永遠都係撚最乞人憎 肥婆都成日講是非八卦野、態度又差、語氣又差<br />\n<br />\n我之前遇過嘅所有肥婆同學都係咁，同事大部份都係、肥婆嘅上級永遠都係好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有相同經歷？<br />\n<br />\n利申：非歧視、有遇過Nice嘅肥婆"},{"pid":"b35784b026ab393029adad33c7cea2463a48eba7","tid":2191842,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"其實肥婆好慘<br />\n成日比人笑"},{"pid":"fd67266449381a6d8bc97b06d54ff1e6cf9a227b","tid":2191842,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"42627fba464932c78efe598897eea786c19f7796","tid":2191842,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b35784b026ab393029adad33c7cea2463a48eba7","tid":2191842,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"其實肥婆好慘<br />\n成日比人笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"以為上水牛牛潮文"},{"pid":"b481752a4c234d594c708d85a95276f60d49101f","tid":2191842,"uid":371912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b35784b026ab393029adad33c7cea2463a48eba7","tid":2191842,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"其實肥婆好慘<br />\n成日比人笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"真心冇諗住歧視佢哋 但係真係覺得佢哋大部份都特別麻煩 利申 有肥婆fd"},{"pid":"35f7f3a2706504fd808f5c02f699a1aaf3a03e4e","tid":2191842,"uid":23531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:32:23.000Z","msg":"醜樣係天生，但係肥冇藉口<br />\n肥人係抵俾人笑，因為佢地自甘墮落"},{"pid":"08d6bf7d3581014903c475ecf0523